1
00:00:00,120 --> 00:00:01,240
Awak tak tahu siapa dia.

2
00:00:01,320 --> 00:00:02,880
Macam mana awak boleh sayang dia?

3
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:04,640
Apa kata kita kenal
antara satu sama lain sekarang?

4
00:00:04,760 --> 00:00:06,200
Awak jaga belakang saya.

5
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:07,440
Saya jaga belakang awak.

6
00:00:07,520 --> 00:00:08,040
Nana.

7
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:09,360
Tolong siasat U untuk saya.

8
00:00:09,560 --> 00:00:10,680
Awak ingat awak buat apa?

9
00:00:10,840 --> 00:00:12,760
Ini sangat biadab pada saya
dan suami saya!

10
00:00:13,280 --> 00:00:13,720
Pai.

11
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:14,680
Saya nak bersendirian sekarang.

12
00:00:14,720 --> 00:00:16,080
Saya takkan biarkan itu berlaku.

13
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:16,760
Mari sini.

14
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:19,080
Awak comel bila marah.

15
00:00:19,280 --> 00:00:21,160
Awak sedih sebab apa yang saya cakap?

16
00:00:24,680 --> 00:00:27,000
Muka awak macam anak itik kecil
bila awak sedih.

17
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:29,800
Jangan sedih lagi, faham?

18
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:34,920
Jadi?

19
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:36,560
Semua okey di sana sekarang?

20
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:41,200
Pai makan ubat tahan sakit dan tidur.

21
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:44,040
Sama juga di sini.

22
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,600
Sepupu-sepupu ni comel, kan?

23
00:00:49,120 --> 00:00:50,120
Hentikan mengarut tu!

24
00:00:51,120 --> 00:00:52,960
Awak tak tahu ke
sejak awak muncul,

25
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:55,200
Pai hampir tak fikir pasal kahwin.

26
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:56,400
Ini menjejaskan saya!

27
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,200
Kalau begitu, tolong saya.

28
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:02,000
Bila Encik Pai dan North berhenti bergaduh,

29
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,360
kita berdua boleh buat hal masing-masing.

30
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:07,120
Cara fikir macam tu tak jalan pada Pai.

31
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,720
Jadi cara mana yang jalan,
teman lelaki Encik Pai?

32
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,560
Dengar sini.

33
00:01:13,240 --> 00:01:16,000
Pai tak percaya awak
sebab dia tak kenal awak.

34
00:01:16,360 --> 00:01:19,800
Lagi jauh awak bawa North dari dia,
lagi dia risau.

35
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,160
Awak kena dapatkan kepercayaan dia.

36
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,040
Itu cara kita tamatkan semua ni, faham?

37
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,800
Macam mana saya nak buat begitu?

38
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:31,360
Dia pun tak nak pandang saya.

39
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,240
Saya ada idea.

40
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,120
Tapi kita kena mula esok.

41
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:42,760
Sasaran kita tengah lemah sekarang.

42
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,640
Inilah masa kita serang dan tewaskan mereka.

43
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,240
Okey.

44
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,640
Apa rancangannya?

45
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:06,160
North.

46
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:07,160
North.

47
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,160
Bangun.

48
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:09,480
Pergi bersiap.

49
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:13,720
Boleh tak bagi saya sejam lagi?

50
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,680
Jom pergi cakap dengan Encik Pai.

51
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,240
Nak cakap apa lagi?

52
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,160
Kita dah okey, kan?

53
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,360
Bagi awak semuanya okey,

54
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,560
tapi nampaknya bukan bagi saya.

55
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,560
Saya pun nak ambil hati dia, tahu?

56
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,280
Tak perlu pun.

57
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,240
Menyusahkan saja.

58
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:41,080
Lebih baik kita jauhkan diri dari dia.

59
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,360
Tunggu.

60
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,040
North.

61
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:47,760
Fikirkan.

62
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,400
Lagi lama kita rahsiakan hubungan kita
daripada Atuk,

63
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:51,960
lagi teruk dia akan fikir pasal kita.

64
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,280
Kalau kita nak bercinta secara terbuka
depan Atuk,

65
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,800
kita kena lepas hal Encik Pai dulu.

66
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,240
Tolonglah?

67
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,640
Tak boleh tidur lagi.

68
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,800
Saya tak nak jadi suami rahsia awak.

69
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:04,000
Saya nak jadi suami
yang awak boleh banggakan.

70
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:04,880
Tolonglah?

71
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:12,120
Baiklah.

72
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:15,120
Kalau begitu, jom pakaikan awak.

73
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,520
Biar saya tidur sekejap lagi dulu.

74
00:04:16,520 --> 00:04:17,640
Saya masih penat.

75
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:19,960
Kalau begitu, saya teman awak.

76
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,720
Hei, ingatkan kita nak tidur.

77
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,520
Baik.

78
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:53,280
(North setuju. Hari ini kita ke pejabatnya.)

79
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,600
Awak nak pergi mana hari ini, sayang?

80
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:08,880
Awak bangun awal.

81
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:15,120
Kita ada janji dengan Nana
pasal perancang perkahwinan.

82
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:16,600
Ya, betul.

83
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:21,520
Saya sibuk risau pasal North
jadi saya... terlupa.

84
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:24,920
Tak apa.

85
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,000
Saya faham.

86
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,200
Saya tahu awak penat.

87
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,680
Boleh kita macam ni sekejap?

88
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,920
Semalam kepala saya sakit sangat.

89
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,560
Ini rasa selesa.

90
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,680
Jangan berhenti, sayang.

91
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,600
Kenapa?

92
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,120
Oh...

93
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:09,000
Cuma awak biasanya tak begitu manja.

94
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:11,040
Saya tak tahu nak buat apa.

95
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,120
Saya dah cakap saya cuma penat.

96
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,240
Kenapa dengan awak?

97
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,000
Saya?

98
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:20,960
Muka awak nampak kekok.

99
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,840
Macam masa kita mula bercinta dulu.

100
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:25,760
Kekok?

101
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,040
Kenapa pula saya kekok?

102
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:33,080
Tapi tengok awak,
tangan asyik buat-buat sibuk.

103
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,520
Tapi kenapa saya nak kekok?

104
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,640
Sepatutnya saya yang tanya.

105
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:50,840
Oh!

106
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,640
Tengok saya.

107
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:55,280
Rambut saya serabut. Mata bengkak.
Hidung pun merah.

108
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,160
Kenapa awak tak cakap apa-apa?

109
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,000
Sebab tak ada apa nak cakap.

110
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,360
Awak nampak comel.

111
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,800
Awak pelik sangat.

112
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,200
Pelik?

113
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,720
Saya tak pelik.

114
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,600
Ini tak pelik.

115
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:14,600
Awak perlukan bantuan saya untuk itu?

116
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:15,520
Saya boleh buat.

117
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:16,320
Saya memang boleh buat.

118
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,320
Awak pergi bersiap.

119
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,120
Pakai tali pinggang elok-elok.

120
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,360
Zip seluar awak terbuka.

121
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:21,280
Pai!

122
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,520
Pakai baju elok-elok.

123
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,280
Awak pun pergilah bersiap.

124
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:27,080
Saya tunggu di luar.

125
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,320
Bye.

126
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:34,360
Terus ke depan.

127
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,440
Tolong hati-hati.

128
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:37,160
Fail-fail itu penting.

129
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,400
Tolong buat dengan cermat.

130
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,040
Belok kiri.

131
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:43,840
Oh, maaf. Biliknya di sebelah kanan.

132
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,280
Tuan, hati-hati dengan gambar itu.

133
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:45,760
Nana.

134
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:46,760
Ya?

135
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,080
Apa yang berlaku?

136
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:52,520
Puan Kia nak buat
pejabat peribadinya di sini.

137
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:53,960
Kenapa?

138
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:57,160
Saya tak tahu, tuan.

139
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:03,280
Kenapa muka masam?

140
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,160
Bukan itu bagus?

141
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,520
Mak Cik Kia akan jauh
dari pejabat tuan mulai sekarang.

142
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,080
Sebenarnya itu bukan perkara buruk.

143
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:15,080
Jangan saling mengganggu
supaya kita tak perlu bergaduh.

144
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,320
Dia cuma ambil berat pasal kamu semua.

145
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:20,360
Itu saja cara dia tunjuk dia peduli.

146
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,120
Jangan risau pasal itu.

147
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:29,480
Nak jadi separuh sabar macam awak, sayang.

148
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,360
Jom mula kerja, boleh?

149
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,040
"Sayang."

150
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:37,160
Nana.

151
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:38,200
Ya.

152
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,000
Ini.

153
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,960
Saya pilih perancang yang pernah urus majlis

154
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:45,880
untuk selebriti, ahli politik dan ahli bisnes.

155
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:49,520
Saya jamin mereka buat terbaik untuk kahwin Encik Tim.

156
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:52,080
Saya hadir hampir semua majlis ini.

157
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,680
Mereka cuma kisah pasal imej.

158
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:58,720
Menangis pun, semua kena berlagak elok untuk foto.

159
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:01,200
Boleh cari perancang yang lebih ikhlas?

160
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,240
Boleh.

161
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,440
Yang ceria dan ikhl—

162
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:15,920
Patutnya ketuk dulu.

163
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:18,200
Saya tak sangka mak cik pun perlu.

164
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:21,000
Atuk pun buat.

165
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:23,120
Baiklah, ya, tentu.

166
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:26,280
Dalam syarikat ni, tiada siapa lebih tinggi dari awak, Pai.

167
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:29,360
Awak boleh arah sesiapa, atau buat tak nampak pun.

168
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:30,440
Termasuk Tuan Besar.

169
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:35,040
Apa kata mak cik cakap saja tujuan mak cik?

170
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:39,840
Mulai sekarang, saya akan kerja di sini.

171
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:47,560
Saya dengar kerja kebelakangan ni diabaikan sebab seronok sendiri.

172
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:48,800
Saya tak pernah buat begitu.

173
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,120
Macam mana awak tahu, Pai,

174
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:56,720
sedangkan tiada siapa berani bantah atau tegur awak?

175
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,600
Mestilah depan awak semua kata awak buat kerja bagus.

176
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:02,440
Belakang awak, semua mengeluh dah muak dengan awak.

177
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,760
Bukan saya, tuan!

178
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:06,000
Saya tak pernah muak!

179
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:09,720
Kalau bukan sebab duit awak, siapa nak tahan awak?

180
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:12,000
Saya terpaksa korbankan masa untuk jaga—

181
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:14,760
Kalau menyusahkan, jauhkan diri saja, mak cik.

182
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:22,360
Tiada siapa bantah Pai sebab mereka hormat pertimbangannya.

183
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,480
Mak cik pun patut cuba begitu,

184
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:26,200
kalau mak cik masih tahu adabnya.

185
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:29,400
Nana.

186
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:30,360
Ya?

187
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:32,360
Bawa Mak Cik Kia ke bilik mesyuarat.

188
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:33,960
Da Zhan.

189
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:34,960
Jom.

190
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:36,760
Da Zhan.

191
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,480
Pergi dulu.

192
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:39,720
Biar orang dewasa berbincang.

193
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:41,880
Silakan ikut sini.

194
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:43,320
Tak perlu teman. Saya tahu jalan.

195
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:56,360
Sayang.

196
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,080
Awak okey?

197
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:01,760
Saya okey.

198
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:05,040
Saya keluar sekejap ambil angin.

199
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:31,960
Maaf, Pai.

200
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:35,040
Saya akan minta maaf pada Mak Cik Kia sekarang.

201
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,600
Ambil masa dulu sampai awak rasa lega.

202
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:43,880
Saya rasa teruk.

203
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:46,120
Awak tak perlu tengok semua tu.

204
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:50,200
Awak betul-betul buat saya terkejut.

205
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,400
Itu bukan macam awak.

206
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:57,840
Saya janji takkan jadi lagi.

207
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,880
Mak Cik Kia memang menyakitkan hati.

208
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:09,280
Lama juga awak tahan sebelum meletup.

209
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,840
Itu pun awak dah cukup tenang.

210
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:13,440
Awak...

211
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,320
Tak marah saya?

212
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,200
Awak nampak tenang gila.

213
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:21,120
Awak patut marah lebih kerap.

214
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,560
Ini bukan masa nak bergurau, tahu?

215
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,080
Baik.

216
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:31,640
Sejujurnya, macam saya baru kenal awak lebih lagi.

217
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:33,440
Saya suka.

218
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:55,960
Sial.

219
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:56,600
Apa hal?

220
00:12:56,800 --> 00:12:57,840
Apa yang tak kena dengan aku?

221
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,360
Tim yang orang kenal tu tenang dan terkawal,

222
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:02,440
tapi aku pula meletup macam tu.

223
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:07,640
Kau biar fikiran mengganggu menang, ya.

224
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,280
Aku nampak macam nak gelak ke?

225
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:13,880
Jadi, lepas dia nampak perangai buruk kau—

226
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:19,200
Maksud aku, lepas dia nampak "warna sebenar" kau, dia macam mana?

227
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,200
Dia suka.

228
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,000
Begitulah.

229
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:34,120
Nah, kan.

230
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:36,680
Nampaknya seorang lagi peminat "red flag".

231
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,040
Kau tahu tak?

232
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:38,560
Pedulikan.

233
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,680
Aku janji takkan hilang kawalan macam tu lagi.

234
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:45,120
Tapi apa yang buat kau meletup?

235
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,040
Mak cik dia tu asyik membebel, kan?

236
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,200
Tapi Pai penat hari ni.

237
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,000
Semalam dia lalui sesuatu.

238
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:54,520
Dia hampir tak tidur dan kepala dia sakit.

239
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:55,760
Kau tak rasa itu buat orang geram?

240
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:58,280
Tak boleh ke dia bagi teman lelaki aku seminit pun tenang?

241
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:00,680
Saudara.

242
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:02,960
Sedarlah.

243
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:06,400
Sekarang kau panggil dia "teman lelaki"?

244
00:14:08,040 --> 00:14:09,040
Bukan "sasaran" kau?

245
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,440
"Sasaran" konon.

246
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:11,880
Ini bukan memanah pun.

247
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:13,640
Berani kau melawan cakap aku?

248
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:14,280
Hati-hati.

249
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:15,720
- Ha, cubalah.
- Ya?

250
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,600
Aku tak takut kau.

251
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:17,640
Apa?

252
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:23,480
Aku rasa kau sedar kau dah mula lembut dengan dia

253
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:24,880
dan kau perlukan aku untuk sedarkan kau.

254
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:27,000
Baik.

255
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,440
Aku tampar bagi kau sedar.

256
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:31,000
Apa?

257
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:34,880
Apa tu?

258
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:41,200
Eh, kenapa pula kau rosakkan macam tu—

259
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:45,320
Jangan. Jatuh. Cinta. Pada. Sasaran kau.

260
00:14:45,640 --> 00:14:46,600
Walau apa pun!

261
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:48,760
Aku... aku tak—

262
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:53,000
Sama-sama.

263
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:55,800
Aku tak jatuh cinta pada sasaran aku.

264
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,160
Aku cuma...

265
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:03,120
memandang dia lain sebab aku nampak sisi dia yang...

266
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:20,520
Sisi dia yang buat aku rasa nak lindungi.

267
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:23,680
Tapi perasaan aku tak berubah.

268
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:25,680
Ya.

269
00:15:26,800 --> 00:15:28,560
Kalau macam tu, baguslah.

270
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:33,200
Tapi dengar perkataan "nak lindungi" keluar dari mulut kau.

271
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:35,720
Itu takkan jadi petanda baik.

272
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:48,520
Hong.

273
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,520
Kenapa dengan kau hari ni?

274
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:51,600
Kau bosan ke?

275
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:53,360
Kau diam sangat.

276
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,160
Ha?

277
00:15:56,680 --> 00:15:58,120
Kau tak dengar, kan?

278
00:15:58,280 --> 00:15:59,640
Maaf.

279
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:02,040
Kebetulan banyak benda dalam fikiran aku kebelakangan ni.

280
00:16:03,680 --> 00:16:06,160
Kau ada masalah ke?

281
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,680
Kau boleh cerita pada aku.

282
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:13,480
Untuk kau, aku sanggup tolong apa saja yang aku mampu.

283
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:16,200
Kau baik sangat sampai risau pasal aku.

284
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:18,280
Kalau macam ni, aku boleh jatuh cinta habis-habisan dengan kau.

285
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,560
Aduh, Hong.

286
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:22,640
Mulut kau semanis muka kau!

287
00:16:22,640 --> 00:16:25,560
Comelnya kau!

288
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:28,840
Oh?

289
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,080
Hong.

290
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:32,440
Aku kena angkat panggilan ni.

291
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:33,880
- Mestilah.
- Aku datang semula sekejap lagi.

292
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,160
Mestilah, Airy.

293
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:01,160
Pak cik, belikan saya patung comel tu.

294
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:04,480
"Pak cik"?

295
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,080
Budak.

296
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,760
Boleh bagi Pak Cik yang ini?

297
00:17:16,080 --> 00:17:17,920
Kau pilih mana-mana satu.

298
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:18,680
Mungkin yang ini?

299
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,360
Yang ini lebih besar.

300
00:17:19,360 --> 00:17:19,880
Atau yang ini?

301
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:20,680
Saya nak yang ini.

302
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:22,520
Tak boleh.

303
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,480
Dah cakap saya nak itu!

304
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:29,840
Yang ini berapa?

305
00:17:30,320 --> 00:17:30,640
Anak aku!

306
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,440
Kau tak apa-apa?

307
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:33,000
Jom pergi kedai lain.

308
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:39,800
Hong.

309
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:40,200
Ya?

310
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,600
Semua okey?

311
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:43,360
Ya, okey.

312
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:46,680
Oh, ini untuk saya?

313
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,400
Bukan!

314
00:17:48,840 --> 00:17:52,040
Oh, maksud saya, awak tak layak
dapat patung macam ini.

315
00:17:52,360 --> 00:17:55,560
Awak layak dapat yang
lebih comel dan cantik.

316
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:59,320
Kalau bukan untuk saya, untuk siapa?

317
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:02,200
Untuk budak di kawasan rumah saya.

318
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:05,000
Kebetulan muka dia
sebiji macam patung ini.

319
00:18:05,080 --> 00:18:06,360
Jadi saya ingat nak belikan untuk dia.

320
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:10,640
Oh, jadi awak sayang sangat
budak entah siapa itu?

321
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:17,920
Kalau awak tak sayang dia, benda begini
takkan buat awak teringat dia.

322
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:21,080
Faham.

323
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:24,600
Hong, saya nak sesuatu di sana.

324
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:25,560
Teman saya beli-belah.

325
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:27,120
Jom beli-belah, ya?

326
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:48,160
Bila sedih, muka awak macam
anak itik kecil.

327
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:49,920
Anak itik?

328
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:51,200
Ya.

329
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,480
Tak ada apa-apa lagi hari ini, kan?

330
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:17,040
Ada.

331
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:20,040
Encik North nak jumpa Encik Pai.

332
00:19:20,760 --> 00:19:21,880
North nak bercakap dengan saya?

333
00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:22,560
Ya.

334
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:25,880
Encik North tunggu di luar, dengan Encik U.

335
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,280
Perlu saya bawa mereka masuk?

336
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:29,400
Bawa—

337
00:19:30,560 --> 00:19:32,560
Kami tunggu lama sangat!

338
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:34,040
Kau patut ketuk dulu.

339
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:37,360
Saya tak tahu kena buat begitu.

340
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:41,160
Apa yang kau nak cakap dengan saya?

341
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:42,640
Saya tak ada.

342
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:44,120
U yang nak.

343
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:45,240
Teruskan.

344
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:49,520
Saya nak jemput awak
makan malam di rumah.

345
00:19:49,640 --> 00:19:52,120
Kita buat majlis kecil
dan masak sesuatu.

346
00:19:52,320 --> 00:19:53,520
Kita boleh kenal lebih rapat.

347
00:19:54,360 --> 00:19:55,640
Saya tengok dulu kalau saya lapang.

348
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,280
Awak saja pilih hari.

349
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:01,800
Kalau tunggu awak, takkan jadi-jadi.

350
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,120
Encik Pai boleh pilih mana-mana hari.

351
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,120
Kami okey saja apa-apa.

352
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:05,760
Faham.

353
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:07,840
Saya rasa saya tak lapang langsung tahun ini.

354
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:08,920
Mungkin tahun depan.

355
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:12,760
Cik Nana.

356
00:20:12,760 --> 00:20:13,280
Ya!

357
00:20:15,360 --> 00:20:16,040
Oh...

358
00:20:18,360 --> 00:20:22,200
Encik Pai sibuk sepanjang bulan ini.

359
00:20:26,360 --> 00:20:27,120
Kalau malam ini?

360
00:20:27,320 --> 00:20:28,080
Bila-bila pun boleh.

361
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,800
Tak terlalu cepat ke, North?

362
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:32,480
Dia betul, North.

363
00:20:33,120 --> 00:20:34,240
Pai habis kerja pukul berapa malam ini?

364
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,400
Pukul tujuh setengah.

365
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,840
Jumpa di rumah U pukul 8.30.

366
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:39,520
- North!
- Apa?

367
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:40,840
Dah putus!

368
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:52,840
Apa?

369
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,080
Mama cuma lapang pukul 8?

370
00:20:58,080 --> 00:21:00,160
Boleh telefon agensi hartanah
untuk uruskan rumah dulu?

371
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,800
(Baik.)

372
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:04,840
(Nasib baik saya ambil gambar
barang letak di mana.)

373
00:21:04,840 --> 00:21:05,680
(Saya uruskan.)

374
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:06,240
Baik.

375
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:07,280
Terima kasih.

376
00:21:07,600 --> 00:21:08,000
Jumpa nanti.

377
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:17,000
North.

378
00:21:17,840 --> 00:21:19,640
Siap ada kelapa, U. Tengok.

379
00:21:21,760 --> 00:21:22,560
Semua ini untuk apa?

380
00:21:23,080 --> 00:21:23,880
Kita nak buat apa?

381
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:25,480
Tak tahu.

382
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:26,840
Saya ambil semua, mana tahu perlu.

383
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:30,880
Kau rasa kita boleh buat apa
dengan semua ini?

384
00:21:32,120 --> 00:21:32,480
Err...

385
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:35,880
Tak tahu.

386
00:21:36,480 --> 00:21:37,080
Saya tak masak.

387
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:38,000
Oh?

388
00:21:38,760 --> 00:21:39,120
Oh?

389
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:40,600
Oh.

390
00:21:46,520 --> 00:21:50,120
Dua peria, tulang rusuk khinzir muda,
lada putih sebiji,

391
00:21:51,360 --> 00:21:52,320
dan bawang putih cincang.

392
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:53,880
...Bawang putih.

393
00:21:54,120 --> 00:21:54,800
Ya, tuan.

394
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:58,880
Masuk.

395
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:04,720
Oh, tak perlu ketuk, sayang.

396
00:22:05,560 --> 00:22:06,240
Tak apa.

397
00:22:07,040 --> 00:22:08,720
Awak buat apa?

398
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:12,280
Saya dapat mesej awak kata
kita makan malam di rumah U.

399
00:22:12,280 --> 00:22:13,040
Apa cerita itu?

400
00:22:15,520 --> 00:22:16,800
North paksa saya.

401
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:19,360
Jadi saya fikir baik saya
tunjuk hidangan terbaik saya.

402
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:21,760
Saya pergi sediakan bahan untuk tuan.

403
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:28,400
Awak nak masak?

404
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:31,800
Jangan kata awak akhirnya mengalah.

405
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:33,920
Tak.

406
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:37,280
Ini peluang untuk tunjuk pada North yang

407
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:40,480
U tak boleh jaga dia
sebaik keluarga kita.

408
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:45,640
Sup herba peria ini tiada tandingan.

409
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:58,160
TUTUP!

410
00:22:59,840 --> 00:23:01,560
Kawan awak cef pastri, kan?

411
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:03,800
Dia boleh buat apa saja.

412
00:23:04,360 --> 00:23:08,560
Menu minuman dan pencuci mulut tempat ini
semua dia yang buat.

413
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:10,200
Mestilah begitu

414
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:13,160
bila pasangan macam awak tak pernah
muncul pun.

415
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:14,880
Saya sampai kena mop lantai sendiri.

416
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:17,040
Biar saya tengok.

417
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:22,840
Hebat.

418
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:27,240
Akhirnya awak buat ikan goreng sempurna
lepas lima kali cuba.

419
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:30,880
Kalau saya tahu awak bazirkan siakap itu,
saya suruh awak latihan guna tilapia.

420
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:35,280
Saya gementar.

421
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,280
Biar saya rasa.

422
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:55,640
Jom.

423
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,440
Kenapa?

424
00:24:07,600 --> 00:24:10,360
Saya tahu kita belum mula,
tapi saya dah penat.

425
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:14,640
Apa kata kita cabut saja?

426
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:16,160
North, tunggu.

427
00:24:16,560 --> 00:24:18,720
Kita dah berlatih.
Tak perlu cabut.

428
00:24:19,520 --> 00:24:20,040
Duduk sini.

429
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:23,480
U, bukan masak yang buat saya penat.

430
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:29,120
Baru fikir nak berbual panjang
dengan Pai pun

431
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:31,240
dah buat saya penat.

432
00:24:35,120 --> 00:24:37,920
Boleh saya tanya jujur?

433
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:41,040
Kenapa awak asyik elak dia?

434
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:57,320
Wah.

435
00:24:57,720 --> 00:24:58,920
Limau separuh guna yang ada merata-rata.

436
00:24:59,320 --> 00:25:00,360
Memang kemas betul
mereka susun tempat ini.

437
00:25:03,080 --> 00:25:03,920
Saya ambilkan.

438
00:25:04,320 --> 00:25:04,680
Okey.

439
00:25:11,840 --> 00:25:12,880
Masuklah.

440
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:21,080
Silakan masuk.

441
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:22,680
Silakan.

442
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:26,920
Helo.

443
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,480
Macam mana trafik?

444
00:25:29,520 --> 00:25:30,120
Biasalah.

445
00:25:31,680 --> 00:25:33,280
North, tandas dekat mana?

446
00:25:33,560 --> 00:25:34,520
- Dia...
- Di sana.

447
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:39,840
Sayang.

448
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:40,720
Ya?

449
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:41,800
Macam mana awak tahu?

450
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:46,120
Maksud saya, pelan rumah biasa.

451
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:48,160
Masuk saja, tandas biasanya bilik pertama
yang nampak.

452
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:49,080
Kenapa awak tak pergi?

453
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:50,200
Cepatlah.

454
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:50,960
Pergilah.

455
00:26:02,240 --> 00:26:03,240
Mak awak mana, U?

456
00:26:04,600 --> 00:26:06,880
Oh, mak pergi Chiang Mai
dengan kawan-kawan.

457
00:26:07,520 --> 00:26:08,960
Tapi dia nak naik penerbangan balik.

458
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:11,320
Oh, sayang Chiang
tak dapat tinggal lama.

459
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:13,680
Apa yang awak bawa tu?

460
00:26:14,520 --> 00:26:15,760
Pai kata dia nak masak.

461
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:16,880
Ini bahan-bahannya.

462
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:28,400
Awak pandai masak?

463
00:26:29,560 --> 00:26:30,440
Sikit.

464
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:33,360
Kalau macam tu, tolong saya.

465
00:26:33,520 --> 00:26:35,560
Kita boleh kenal lebih rapat.

466
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,720
Baik, Encik Pai.

467
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:42,160
North dan Encik Tim,
jemput buat macam rumah sendiri.

468
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:43,360
Tak perlu panggil “Encik”.

469
00:26:47,320 --> 00:26:47,920
Panggil Tim saja.

470
00:26:51,680 --> 00:26:52,240
U.

471
00:26:57,600 --> 00:26:58,560
Baik. Silakan.

472
00:26:58,840 --> 00:26:59,960
Buat yang terbaik.

473
00:27:06,040 --> 00:27:09,360
Awak rasa... mereka akan okey?

474
00:27:09,600 --> 00:27:10,720
Rasanya ya.

475
00:27:11,520 --> 00:27:12,640
Awak nak masuk sekali dengan mereka

476
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:14,040
untuk berjaga-jaga?

477
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:15,200
Ya.

478
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:17,000
Biar saya tolong.

479
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:18,160
Saya pun nak masak.

480
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:19,600
Cepat buat.

481
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:38,400
Saya datang untuk meminang Pai
untuk Tim secara rasmi.

482
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:39,680
Ya ampun!

483
00:27:41,520 --> 00:27:42,000
Sayang?

484
00:27:42,560 --> 00:27:43,040
Ya?

485
00:27:43,280 --> 00:27:43,960
Awak okey?

486
00:27:45,520 --> 00:27:47,640
Oh, ini... Ya ampun!

487
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:48,480
Wah!

488
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:51,400
U memang berbakat, sayang!

489
00:27:52,360 --> 00:27:52,920
Betul ke?

490
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:53,480
Ya.

491
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:54,800
Mari tengok, sayang.

492
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:55,760
Apa?

493
00:27:55,800 --> 00:27:56,400
Tengok.

494
00:27:56,800 --> 00:28:00,040
Dia juara gusti lengan...
masa darjah tiga.

495
00:28:00,320 --> 00:28:02,960
Awak masuk pertandingan gusti lengan
masa sekolah rendah?

496
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:04,200
Ya.

497
00:28:17,760 --> 00:28:18,680
Tunggu.

498
00:28:19,080 --> 00:28:21,000
Siapa pula tekan loceng rumah sendiri?

499
00:28:27,360 --> 00:28:28,080
Sayang.

500
00:28:28,520 --> 00:28:29,120
Y-Ya?

501
00:28:35,320 --> 00:28:36,560
Saya nak kencing.

502
00:28:36,560 --> 00:28:37,200
Saya pergi sekejap.

503
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:38,680
Dah tak tahan.

504
00:28:39,800 --> 00:28:41,280
Sampai meremang semua.

505
00:29:03,080 --> 00:29:04,760
(U dan aku tak boleh ada mak yang sama!)

506
00:29:04,760 --> 00:29:06,440
(Balik. Aku uruskan sini.)

507
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:11,320
Sayang.

508
00:29:11,320 --> 00:29:11,960
Ya?

509
00:29:12,280 --> 00:29:13,000
Kenapa?

510
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:14,640
Oh, tak ada apa.

511
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:18,000
Saya cuma tengok pintu sini
dan saya ingat...

512
00:29:18,760 --> 00:29:22,120
Arkitek tu buat kerja tak kemas.

513
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:24,040
U. U!

514
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:24,920
U, hei!

515
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:25,600
Ya?

516
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:26,800
Awak perlukan bantuan saya?

517
00:29:26,800 --> 00:29:27,480
Tak apa.

518
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:29,640
Saya uruskan. Saya arkitek, ingat?

519
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:31,680
Pai, awak duduk saja. Okey?

520
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:32,160
U!

521
00:29:32,800 --> 00:29:33,240
Apa?

522
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:34,680
Pintu awak rosak.

523
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:36,440
Jom keluar tengok sekejap.

524
00:29:36,800 --> 00:29:37,800
Pintu saya?

525
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,840
Teruk betul buatnya!

526
00:29:44,560 --> 00:29:45,600
Mari sini, awak.

527
00:29:45,840 --> 00:29:46,760
Nyaris tadi.

528
00:29:46,760 --> 00:29:48,160
Kalau aku tak nampak Mama Oom,

529
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:50,680
kita kena reka cerita sedih
konon kita dua saudara terpisah.

530
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:51,400
Sial!

531
00:29:51,440 --> 00:29:52,640
Awak pun upah dia?

532
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:53,200
Ya, memang.

533
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:55,040
Memang nyaris.

534
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:57,280
Sekarang nak buat apa?

535
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:00,720
Aku masuk dulu.

536
00:30:00,840 --> 00:30:02,160
Nanti awak ikut.

537
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:05,280
Awak kena cakap pada Pai
mak awak tak dapat datang.

538
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:06,240
Okey.

539
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:07,880
Dan awak kena biar Pai
lepaskan geram pada awak.

540
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:08,960
Sial.

541
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:10,560
Hampir saja awak rosakkan semuanya.

542
00:30:11,040 --> 00:30:13,480
Nampaknya semua orang
lepaskan geram pada aku sekarang.

543
00:30:16,560 --> 00:30:19,000
Aku boleh tolong, tahu?

544
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,520
Bagi sini.

545
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:22,880
North.

546
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:24,240
Baiklah.

547
00:30:25,560 --> 00:30:26,520
Ada apa-apa saya boleh bantu?

548
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:29,760
Encik Pai.

549
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:32,880
Ada ribut petir besar di Chiang Mai.

550
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:34,840
Penerbangan mak saya ditangguh.

551
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:42,680
Saya tak nak dia terus menunggu
penerbangan macam ni.

552
00:30:44,600 --> 00:30:46,520
Awak patut beritahu mak awak.

553
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:47,880
Baik.

554
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:49,440
Maaf pasal ni.

555
00:30:50,600 --> 00:30:52,160
Saya akan beritahu dia.

556
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:56,600
Dah siap.

557
00:30:56,600 --> 00:30:59,000
Mari tolong saya di dapur.

558
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:00,320
Ya, Encik Pai.

559
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:05,160
North, apa kata awak siapkan meja?

560
00:31:05,360 --> 00:31:08,400
Tapi kalau saya tinggalkan awak berdua
dengan U macam ni,

561
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,920
awak pasti takkan mula bergaduh?

562
00:31:11,840 --> 00:31:13,360
Macam ni, macam mana?

563
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:17,120
Jom susun meja dan makan malam

564
00:31:17,120 --> 00:31:18,800
di laman depan, dekat luar?

565
00:31:19,560 --> 00:31:20,640
Jom, North.

566
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:28,960
Sambung kerja.

567
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:29,760
Ya, tuan.

568
00:31:37,760 --> 00:31:38,800
Jangan risau.

569
00:31:39,320 --> 00:31:40,360
Pai takkan apa-apakan U.

570
00:31:41,560 --> 00:31:43,280
Mana boleh saya tak risau, Tim.

571
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,440
Lupakan pasal mereka nak serasi,

572
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:51,480
nak yakinkan Pai yang U dan saya
betul-betul bercinta pun macam mustahil.

573
00:31:54,400 --> 00:31:56,040
Tapi kenapa awak begitu jatuh cinta?

574
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:57,760
Bukankah kamu baru kenal?

575
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:08,840
Awak dan Pai ambil masa lama
untuk jatuh cinta?

576
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:24,240
Bagi saya, bila saya jatuh cinta,

577
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:35,880
sekejap saja dah tahu
dia istimewa.

578
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:45,240
Dan yang penting
apa yang jadi lepas tu.

579
00:32:47,040 --> 00:32:49,040
Bila awak dah tahu awak suka dia,

580
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:51,760
masa tu awak putuskan
nak cuba atau teruskan hidup.

581
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:59,480
Awak lebih matang daripada sangka, tahu?

582
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:05,360
Awak cuma tengok saya melalui mata Pai.

583
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:07,120
Mestilah saya nampak tak matang.

584
00:33:22,800 --> 00:33:26,440
Untuk hilangkan pahitnya,
salut peria dengan garam

585
00:33:26,440 --> 00:33:28,440
dan sejukkan dalam peti sejuk 20 minit.

586
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:31,120
Boleh masak apa saja
sementara tunggu.

587
00:33:31,520 --> 00:33:32,280
Faham.

588
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:36,320
Saya akan goreng snek
macam nugget dan kentang goreng.

589
00:33:36,560 --> 00:33:38,240
North suka itu.

590
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:41,680
Jangan biar dia makan
benda tak berkhasiat macam tu.

591
00:33:42,560 --> 00:33:46,800
Tapi kalau dia tak suka makanan berkhasiat,

592
00:33:48,280 --> 00:33:51,520
dia tetap makan yang tak sihat
bila sorang-sorang, Encik Pai.

593
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:56,840
Saya cuma...

594
00:34:06,280 --> 00:34:08,520
Apa yang awak suka tentang dia?

595
00:34:08,520 --> 00:34:11,280
Awak dah tahu siapa dia dari awal,
atau baru tahu kemudian?

596
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:14,280
Oh...

597
00:34:14,640 --> 00:34:19,520
Saya baru tahu keluarganya miliki Empire
lepas saya kahwin dengan dia.

598
00:34:20,040 --> 00:34:22,760
Tapi kalau Encik tanya
bila saya jatuh hati...

599
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:24,360
Rasanya bila saya mula berbual dengan dia.

600
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:26,120
Jadi, kenapa?

601
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:29,920
Siapa tak suka orang macam North?

602
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:31,040
Jawab!

603
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,200
Baik.

604
00:34:35,200 --> 00:34:37,440
Saya suka North sebab dia baik.

605
00:34:37,720 --> 00:34:40,160
Dia tak pernah berniat jahat pada sesiapa.

606
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:44,720
Dia jenis orang yang
takkan sakiti sesiapa pun.

607
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:46,480
North terlalu naif.

608
00:34:46,720 --> 00:34:48,280
Kami cuba ubah benda tu pada dia.

609
00:34:48,680 --> 00:34:51,640
Tapi saya rasa dia tak perlu diubah, Encik Pai.

610
00:34:52,080 --> 00:34:55,080
Dia patut bebas
jalani hidup ikut cara dia.

611
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:57,160
Cuma mulai sekarang,
saya akan jaga belakang dia.

612
00:35:00,600 --> 00:35:01,760
Macam mana awak nak buat begitu?

613
00:35:02,640 --> 00:35:04,080
Katakanlah...

614
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:12,320
Kalau North masih percaya Santa Claus,
saya akan jadi Santa tiap tahun.

615
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:14,480
Dia tak percaya pun.

616
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:17,480
Saya yang beritahu dia
Santa Claus tu tak wujud.

617
00:35:18,680 --> 00:35:19,840
Encik Pai.

618
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:23,240
Saya percaya ada
lebih daripada satu cara untuk membesar.

619
00:35:23,720 --> 00:35:28,920
North boleh kenal dunia
tanpa hilang sikap optimis dia.

620
00:35:32,520 --> 00:35:36,480
Dunia jadi indah sebab ada orang macam North,
betul tak?

621
00:35:44,640 --> 00:35:46,200
Jom sambung masak.

622
00:35:57,880 --> 00:36:03,480
Saya minta maaf lagi,
mak saya tak dapat datang makan malam ini.

623
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:05,480
Tak apa.

624
00:36:06,200 --> 00:36:06,880
Cuba rasa.

625
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:09,040
Ya.

626
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:17,760
Sedap macam biasa!

627
00:36:19,040 --> 00:36:21,040
Ini kali pertama
saya makan yang macam ni.

628
00:36:21,080 --> 00:36:24,800
Resipi sup herba ni
rahsia nenek moyang kami.

629
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:28,840
Kami pernah dapat tawaran mahal,
tapi kami tolak untuk jual.

630
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:33,040
Faham.

631
00:36:33,200 --> 00:36:34,360
Awak tahu kenapa?

632
00:36:34,720 --> 00:36:37,000
Kalau saya jawab betul, ada hadiah tak?

633
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:37,560
Jaga mulut.

634
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:39,400
Maaf.

635
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:46,120
Sebab yang terbaik
kami simpan untuk keluarga.

636
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:50,240
Itu moto keluarga kami untuk semua benda.

637
00:36:50,640 --> 00:36:54,560
Sebab tu tak ada siapa jaga kami
lebih baik daripada kami sendiri.

638
00:36:56,400 --> 00:36:57,640
Cukup, Pai.

639
00:36:57,880 --> 00:36:59,600
Kenapa kau asyik buat U takut macam tu?

640
00:37:00,560 --> 00:37:01,880
Aku tak tahu apa yang kau cakap.

641
00:37:02,720 --> 00:37:03,680
Pai.

642
00:37:03,680 --> 00:37:06,680
Jangan layan U macam dia nak culik aku
ke Kutub Utara.

643
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:11,320
Kau tahu tak apa dia cakap pada aku
masa kami sampai tadi?

644
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:19,400
Boleh aku tanya jujur?

645
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:23,120
Kenapa kau asyik elak dia?

646
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:27,560
Sebab Pai terlalu tegas.

647
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:28,240
Kenapa begitu?

648
00:37:28,240 --> 00:37:28,960
U.

649
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:30,440
Kau main-main dengan aku ke?

650
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,560
Mestilah tak.

651
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:37,800
Tapi cuba fikir sekejap,
kenapa jadi macam tu.

652
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:42,160
Aku janji aku takkan cakap apa-apa.

653
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:50,800
Sebab Pai terlalu tegas.

654
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:55,040
Apa saja aku cakap atau buat, semua macam salah.

655
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,320
Pernah sekali aku buat lawak,

656
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:59,600
tapi Pai jadikan benda tu ceramah sejam.

657
00:38:01,240 --> 00:38:02,200
Aku faham—

658
00:38:02,200 --> 00:38:06,200
Dan apa yang aku buat cuma susahkan hidup Pai.

659
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:10,240
Sebab tu aku nak jauhkan diri daripada dia.

660
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:14,560
Supaya apa pun silap aku buat,
aku tanggung sendiri.

661
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:16,640
Aku tak nak jadi beban pada sesiapa.

662
00:38:18,640 --> 00:38:19,400
Aku rasa...

663
00:38:20,240 --> 00:38:22,480
Kau dah keterlaluan sikit

664
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:24,800
sebab kau langsung tak libatkan dia
dalam hidup kau.

665
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:28,080
Dia tak tahu langsung
macam mana kau urus masalah kau.

666
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:31,240
Bila dia tak dapat agak keadaan,

667
00:38:31,240 --> 00:38:33,240
dia rasa perlu ambil alih sendiri
dan selesaikan semua masalah kau.

668
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:37,920
Jadi kalau aku lebih banyak cakap dengan Pai,
dia akan bagi aku ruang?

669
00:38:40,200 --> 00:38:41,120
Aku tak tahu.

670
00:38:41,480 --> 00:38:43,560
Aku cuma rasa itu strategi yang bagus.

671
00:38:43,680 --> 00:38:45,720
Kau dah elak dia,
tapi tak jadi, kan?

672
00:38:46,040 --> 00:38:47,480
Mungkin dah tiba masa ubah cara?

673
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,400
Kita boleh mula hari ini.

674
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:56,960
Dan satu lagi,
U dah berusaha sangat untuk pastikan

675
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:59,520
makan malam ini sempurna.

676
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:02,440
Dia cuma nak buat kau kagum, tahu?

677
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:04,000
Ikan goreng ni,

678
00:39:04,600 --> 00:39:06,520
kami betul-betul baru belajar
cara buatnya hari ini.

679
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:24,360
Kau tak perlu risau U akan bawa aku lari,
Pai.

680
00:39:25,600 --> 00:39:28,600
Sebenarnya U buat yang sebaliknya.

681
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:38,240
Aku... tak pernah pun cakap
aku risau pasal tu.

682
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:39,400
Itu anggapan kau.

683
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:03,800
Terima kasih.

684
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,440
Tak teruk.

685
00:40:22,520 --> 00:40:23,560
Terima kasih.

686
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:26,880
Itu bukan pujian sangat pun.

687
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:31,560
Aku dah gembira ikan ni masak pun.

688
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:32,560
Apa?

689
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,080
Mestilah masak betul, U.

690
00:40:34,080 --> 00:40:35,760
Kau dah banyak kali berlatih, tahu?

691
00:40:36,160 --> 00:40:37,400
Tim, kau pun cuba.

692
00:40:37,720 --> 00:40:38,400
Mestilah.

693
00:40:40,200 --> 00:40:41,520
Biar aku buang tulang ikan untuk kamu semua.

694
00:40:42,120 --> 00:40:43,640
Makan banyak ikan, North.

695
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:48,840
Memandangkan kita semua ada,

696
00:40:50,120 --> 00:40:51,840
aku dah lama nak tahu.

697
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:55,160
Macam mana kamu berdua kenal?

698
00:40:58,000 --> 00:40:59,080
Err...

699
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:01,880
Macam mana kami kenal, ya?

700
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:03,920
Aku yang cerita,
atau kau nak, North?

701
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:05,640
Biar aku yang cerita,

702
00:41:06,080 --> 00:41:10,280
sebab aku tak tahu seteruk mana
kau sangka pasal aku masa mula-mula jumpa.

703
00:41:10,520 --> 00:41:12,160
Tak boleh. Kalau macam tu biar aku cerita.

704
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:13,120
Biar aku cerita.

705
00:41:13,120 --> 00:41:15,480
Macam ni...

706
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:55,080
U.

707
00:41:57,520 --> 00:42:00,920
Semua ni betul-betul sedap,
atau aku je mabuk?

708
00:42:02,520 --> 00:42:03,840
Memang sedap.

709
00:42:03,840 --> 00:42:06,720
Aku tak minum setitik pun,
tapi aku pun seronok.

710
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:10,120
Aku tak percaya.

711
00:42:12,160 --> 00:42:16,200
Aku dah cakap Pai akan dengar
kalau kita cakap elok-elok.

712
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:21,760
Dia cuma perlukan masa untuk terima
sepupu kesayangan dia dah kahwin.

713
00:42:23,960 --> 00:42:26,000
Betul ke kau suami aku?

714
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:27,520
Asyik-asyik kau bela Pai.

715
00:42:27,520 --> 00:42:29,040
Kau dah jadi kawan dia sekarang?

716
00:42:29,840 --> 00:42:34,320
Kau nampak lebih gembira
bila kau tak bergaduh dengan Pai, tahu?

717
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:42,240
Sebenarnya, Pai cakap pada aku

718
00:42:42,240 --> 00:42:45,920
apa yang aku rasa untuk kau bukan cinta.

719
00:42:47,240 --> 00:42:48,920
Dia kata itu cuma ikut rasa saja.

720
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:54,640
Dan aku tak dapat nafikan, aku setuju.

721
00:42:55,240 --> 00:42:56,800
Aku ragu-ragu.

722
00:42:57,640 --> 00:42:59,360
Aku tak tahu kalau semuanya jadi terlalu cepat.

723
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:01,120
Aku tak tahu sama ada ini cinta.

724
00:43:03,120 --> 00:43:07,040
Tapi hari ini betul-betul buat aku sedar yang

725
00:43:07,040 --> 00:43:09,200
aku memang cintakan kau, U.

726
00:43:10,760 --> 00:43:11,680
Oh.

727
00:43:12,080 --> 00:43:13,560
Leganya!

728
00:43:13,560 --> 00:43:15,640
Lain kali boleh tak mula dengan “aku cinta kau”

729
00:43:15,640 --> 00:43:17,200
dulu sebelum sambung yang lain?

730
00:43:17,200 --> 00:43:18,600
Aku sempat takut tadi!

731
00:43:20,200 --> 00:43:21,600
U, sudahlah.

732
00:43:21,640 --> 00:43:24,640
Aku tak boleh tahan.

733
00:43:36,320 --> 00:43:37,480
Seronok hari ini.

734
00:43:37,640 --> 00:43:38,480
Terima kasih.

735
00:43:38,840 --> 00:43:39,680
Mestilah.

736
00:43:40,480 --> 00:43:42,800
Terima kasih untuk hidangan yang sedap.

737
00:43:45,360 --> 00:43:48,320
Jom makan tengah hari
di rumah keluarga kita nanti.

738
00:43:50,280 --> 00:43:51,360
Tunggu!

739
00:43:52,080 --> 00:43:55,240
Maksudnya Pai terima U sekarang?

740
00:43:55,240 --> 00:43:56,000
Ya!

741
00:44:01,840 --> 00:44:05,080
Aku cuma kenalkan dia pada keluarga,
bukan beritahu kamu dah berkahwin.

742
00:44:08,960 --> 00:44:10,480
Terima kasih, Pai.

743
00:44:10,480 --> 00:44:11,600
Ya.

744
00:44:21,920 --> 00:44:23,400
Tahniah, U.

745
00:44:23,760 --> 00:44:24,600
Tahniah.

746
00:44:24,600 --> 00:44:25,200
Baik.

747
00:44:25,680 --> 00:44:26,880
Maaf pasal itu.

748
00:44:27,240 --> 00:44:29,480
Kurangkan sikit, penipu.

749
00:44:34,360 --> 00:44:35,160
Jumpa lagi.

750
00:44:51,520 --> 00:44:52,440
Sayang.

751
00:44:54,280 --> 00:44:56,400
Kalau aku masih percaya Santa Claus,

752
00:44:57,880 --> 00:45:00,680
awak akan cakap benar
atau awak akan

753
00:45:00,680 --> 00:45:03,200
menyamar jadi Santa masa Krismas?

754
00:45:07,480 --> 00:45:10,000
Aku takkan cakap benar,

755
00:45:10,160 --> 00:45:12,680
tapi aku pun takkan menyamar jadi Santa.

756
00:45:12,680 --> 00:45:17,160
Kalau awak sedih sebab tak dapat hadiah
daripada Santa, aku bagi satu.

757
00:45:17,160 --> 00:45:18,480
Awak akan berhenti tunggu Santa

758
00:45:18,480 --> 00:45:20,080
dan tunggu nak jumpa aku pula.

759
00:45:25,160 --> 00:45:29,320
Entah kenapa, awak dan U macam sama.

760
00:45:32,920 --> 00:45:34,000
Macam mana?

761
00:45:37,240 --> 00:45:40,320
Kamu berdua jatuh cinta dulu, dan teruk.

762
00:45:41,040 --> 00:45:44,040
Macam mana rasanya jatuh cinta dulu?

763
00:45:46,160 --> 00:45:49,080
Macam mana rasanya jatuh cinta dulu, ha?

764
00:45:49,080 --> 00:45:54,520
Orang yang jatuh dulu tak nak orang tahu
betapa comelnya orang dia suka.

765
00:45:55,720 --> 00:45:58,280
Dia tak sabar nak pikat orang dia suka
secepat mungkin.

766
00:45:58,360 --> 00:46:02,080
Bila dah jadi, dia nak pastikan
semua jadi elok antara mereka,

767
00:46:02,360 --> 00:46:04,880
sebab dia yakin dalam hati,
tak mungkin orang lain untuk dia.

768
00:46:04,880 --> 00:46:06,640
Awak melebih-lebih.

769
00:46:06,720 --> 00:46:08,160
Tak.

770
00:46:08,360 --> 00:46:09,720
Aku serius.

771
00:46:10,400 --> 00:46:12,200
Aku sayang awak sangat, tahu?

772
00:46:12,920 --> 00:46:14,120
Aku tahu.

773
00:46:15,160 --> 00:46:16,240
Ini dah jelaskan semuanya.

774
00:46:16,240 --> 00:46:17,440
Aku faham.

775
00:46:32,280 --> 00:46:35,720
U pandang North macam awak pandang aku.

776
00:46:44,320 --> 00:46:45,360
Sayang.

777
00:46:45,760 --> 00:46:46,800
Beg apa tu?

778
00:46:49,360 --> 00:46:50,400
Aku hampir terlupa.

779
00:46:53,880 --> 00:46:57,200
Aku jumpa ini hari ini, teringat awak,
jadi aku belikan untuk awak.

780
00:47:03,120 --> 00:47:04,240
Anak itik?

781
00:47:06,120 --> 00:47:07,600
Comelnya!

782
00:47:07,760 --> 00:47:08,800
Cuba tengok.

783
00:47:09,160 --> 00:47:10,920
Muka dia sama macam awak.

784
00:47:11,200 --> 00:47:12,400
Taklah.

785
00:47:12,400 --> 00:47:13,400
Pulangkan balik.

786
00:47:16,240 --> 00:47:18,800
Awak betul-betul buat aku terasa hati.

787
00:47:19,840 --> 00:47:20,800
Betul?

788
00:47:22,920 --> 00:47:23,880
Baiklah.

789
00:47:24,200 --> 00:47:25,200
Okey, aku akui dia comel.

790
00:47:30,240 --> 00:47:32,040
Jom balik.

791
00:47:41,880 --> 00:47:44,400
Kita betul-betul berjaya.

792
00:47:47,760 --> 00:47:50,280
Lepas ni tak ada apa nak dirisaukan,
kan?

793
00:47:50,840 --> 00:47:53,360
Pai paling susah nak puaskan hati.

794
00:47:54,960 --> 00:47:57,480
Kalau kita tak perlu rahsiakan lagi,

795
00:47:58,120 --> 00:48:00,000
awak nak majlis kahwin, North?

796
00:48:02,080 --> 00:48:04,480
Mula-mula, aku tak nak.

797
00:48:06,360 --> 00:48:11,880
Tapi aku rasa awak akan segak jadi
pengantin, dan aku tak sabar nak yang besar!

798
00:48:12,560 --> 00:48:13,720
Yang besar?

799
00:48:13,720 --> 00:48:16,040
Aku nak video kahwin yang kelakar.

800
00:48:16,040 --> 00:48:17,760
Kawan aku, Pure, boleh
buat kek kahwin kita.

801
00:48:17,760 --> 00:48:20,040
Itu bagus untuk PR
kedai roti kita juga.

802
00:48:20,120 --> 00:48:20,920
Dan sut?

803
00:48:20,920 --> 00:48:22,400
Aku pakai putih, awak pakai hitam.

804
00:48:22,880 --> 00:48:25,400
Hari tu aku akan menyanyi untuk awak,
sebagai kejutan.

805
00:48:25,400 --> 00:48:26,840
Jangan, jangan beritahu aku!

806
00:48:27,280 --> 00:48:29,400
Nanti tak jadi kejutan.

807
00:48:29,400 --> 00:48:31,720
Tapi awak tak tahu
lagu apa aku nak nyanyi, kan?

808
00:48:32,120 --> 00:48:33,640
Tapi aku dah tahu awak memang akan!

809
00:48:33,640 --> 00:48:34,760
Kalau macam tu, aku tak nyanyi.

810
00:48:35,000 --> 00:48:36,920
Tunggu, aku dah letak harapan tinggi.

811
00:48:38,240 --> 00:48:40,320
Awak serius pasal semua ni, kan?

812
00:48:41,320 --> 00:48:43,480
Sebenarnya semua ni kedengaran seronok.

813
00:48:43,800 --> 00:48:46,800
Rasanya kita kena tunggu Pai selesaikan
dulu sebelum kita teruskan.

814
00:48:47,000 --> 00:48:47,960
Itu beberapa bulan lagi.

815
00:48:47,960 --> 00:48:50,000
Majlis kita patut, macam,
seminggu lepas majlis dia!

816
00:48:50,720 --> 00:48:51,480
Oh, secepat itu?

817
00:48:51,480 --> 00:48:52,680
Secepat itu!

818
00:48:55,920 --> 00:48:57,160
Ini bagus.

819
00:48:58,160 --> 00:49:01,840
Macam hari ini baru aku ada keluarga.

820
00:49:04,000 --> 00:49:05,320
Aku pun.

821
00:49:19,640 --> 00:49:21,160
Aku sayang awak, North.

822
00:49:30,320 --> 00:49:32,200
Aku sayang awak juga, U.

823
00:49:36,880 --> 00:49:38,000
U!

824
00:49:57,960 --> 00:49:59,120
Awak nampak tertekan, sayang.

825
00:49:59,120 --> 00:49:59,680
Apa?

826
00:49:59,680 --> 00:50:01,960
Awak tahu awak boleh jujur dengan aku.

827
00:50:01,960 --> 00:50:02,880
Aku...

828
00:50:02,880 --> 00:50:04,960
Kalau kita tak berkahwin secara sah,

829
00:50:04,960 --> 00:50:07,440
maknanya usaha aku sia-sia.

830
00:50:07,440 --> 00:50:08,560
Sekarang aku dah tahu kebenaran.

831
00:50:08,560 --> 00:50:09,960
Awak kena cerai dengan sepupu aku.

832
00:50:10,000 --> 00:50:11,200
Tak, aku tak nak.

833
00:50:11,200 --> 00:50:13,000
Aku akan kekal di sini dengan North.

834
00:50:15,800 --> 00:50:17,680
Awak seluruh dunia aku, Tim.

835
00:50:17,680 --> 00:50:20,360
Aku tak boleh hidup tanpa awak.

